{"tid":1557963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於聽日911既燒山/隨機殺人傷人既謠言, 一切都係關中共事","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:51:56.000Z","uid":125079,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"da357dbf15b76ba11186c46594b06e69b398a6d3","tid":1557963,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依單野真係好好笑, 成班示威者自己冇聽到過既新聞, 反而藍屍建制派中共媒體知道宣傳先</span><br />\n<br />\n針對無辜既傷害大自然, 以及普通人平凡人既性命, 香港市民示威者係會割蓆<br />\n<br />\n連登有班鬼扮示威者, 係度分化, 方法一 : ( 唔係話核彈都唔割 ? ) 挑釁香港人及令到有人以為全部示威者支持 <br />\n<br />\n我係核彈都唔割, 但前題係所做既野針對政府及警狗 <br />\n<br />\n認真單謠言都幾白痴, <span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人連警狗都未夠膽麻包袋, 竟然同我講周圍殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你當示威者弱智? </span><br />\n<br />\n得一個好大既原因, 中共港共抹黑, 連官媒都講埋, 但我身邊冇一個黃絲朋友知, 又或者有人克意去製造恐慌, 又或者逼出緊急法<br />\n<br />\n情境一 聽日有事:<br />\n<br />\n中共港共大把理由話恐襲, 然後順利成章話比國際聽香港示威者係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n但後果呢? 外國同香港人都只會知道係中共自編自導自演, 目的就係好似上面咁抹黑示威者<br />\n<br />\n而如果中共真係做得出, 香港亦都會攬炒, 因為咁做得冇可能冇證據留低, 中共係外國可信度已經係零<br />\n<br />\n我相信一係製造恐慌 ( 特別係藍屍大陸人當中, 因為依加藍屍gp 吹曬風, 大陸官媒報埋, 反而香港人黃既冇乜邊個知) , 好似 722咁, 黑社會出現, 成個新界西夜晚冇人敢出黎, 班藍屍聽日一定信到十足十, 大家預咗聽晚周街都冇藍屍<br />\n<br />\n係中共既詆毀抹黑, 玩緊白色恐怖, 令到香港人提心吊膽, 從而繼續做成民眾壓力逼香港人覺得示威者冷血/殘暴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇事既就: 繼續宣傳示威者恐嚇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1171121438377426944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1171121438377426944&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=16b8b855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1171121438377426944</a><br />\n<br />\n送條 Twitter link 比大家"},{"pid":"71dc96ce2742b3c8ece47ea4fdf8703bbe088de7","tid":1557963,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"外國已經有人覺聽日單既宣傳又係中共搞出黎"},{"pid":"047a900e229ee974561ecbc69b7131e82c484012","tid":1557963,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">［必睇］呢個時候應立即停止示威，改做文宣。運動將會必勝！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1557504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1557504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47101ade069cfbbe0541135e05ebd35fabedc204","tid":1557963,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071f3373352d213821d05faad55c344fbf965f9d","tid":1557963,"uid":277084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1Me08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1Me08.png&h=80eecf12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲之文宣咗先"},{"pid":"c6bbf1b98d197d4c41d1d2a4efcb4818da4dd594","tid":1557963,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"求文宣 趁依家影印鋪未關好去貼"},{"pid":"85ad476fc6b2dfe1b7f75179353d6d42b7cc30ef","tid":1557963,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"同埋中共搞膽咁做 就香港一定出緊急法<br />\n真攬炒<img src=\"/as